      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHOT OF MAGIC (1) was checked in the run and safely held when fourth (22.70) in a Grade 5 over 400m at Maitland. Has the ability and looks a key chance. ICEBERG AHEAD (3) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 3.5 lengths at Maitland in a handy 22.35 beating Poker Nismo. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Should be in this for a long way. IOMMI (2) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when seventh at this track over 350m behind Fix It Fred (20.51) in a Grade 5. Must be included in calculations. LAMIA MODENA (8) should be thereabouts after filling a top-three at this track and distance most recently.",
